narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You will learn far more researching a topic that interests you for a month than you ever will in your classes!
The senior essay. It's an independent course, no class time.

The English dept. doesn't do much to actively encourage people to write theses, but for all the angst toward the end, I really enjoyed mine. I'd never been challenged to have a forty-page thought before.
I very much enjoyed writing a senior essay.
